<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.4.11">
<l>aḷaviyaṉṟa vēḻulakat tavarperumāṉ kaṇṇaṉai</l>
<l>vaḷavayalcūḻ vaṇkurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ vāynturaitta</l>
<l>vaḷaviyaṉṟa vantāti yāyirattu ḷippattiṉ</l>
<l>vaḷavuraiyāl peṟalākum vāṉōṅku peruvaḷamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one utters the wealth of these ten in the measured Antāti thousand</l>
<l>excellently composed by Catakōpaṉ from liberal Kurukūr surrounded</l>
<l>by fertile paddy fields, on his great lord Kaṇṇaṉ of seven worlds he advanced to measure,</l>
<l>there will be obtaining of profit great to the height of the sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
